title.rendered: Foam Padded Disposable Nose Clip -Pack of 100

excerpt.rendered:
Disposable Nose Clips 100Pk are foam padded and disposable. They are designed for patient comfort and seal on the nose easily.

Disposable Nose Clips 100Pk come in a convenient bulk pack of 100 nose plugs. They fit comfortably while maintaining a seal.

Disposable Nose Clips 100Pk work great for chronic nose bleeds and since they are disposable you can take them wherever you go. Keep some in the car or in your purse in case of emergencies.

Bulk pack includes 100 nose clips Lightweight and ergonomic Plastic with foam nose pieces for added comfort.
